who put me in this chair

38:06.936 --> 38:09.374
got bored of laying low upstate.

38:09.417 --> 38:11.550
So I called
my partner.

38:12.768 --> 38:15.118
He was off the clock,
just helping me out.

38:16.163 --> 38:17.904
I see.He covered

38:17.947 --> 38:20.559
the Utica arrival gate,
I covered Troy.

38:20.602 --> 38:23.039
The scumbag came in from Troy.

38:23.083 --> 38:25.825
He made me
as soon as I rolled up on him.

38:25.868 --> 38:28.044
He got a shot off
and nicked me in the wrist,

38:28.088 --> 38:29.959
while I kneecapped him

38:30.003 --> 38:33.136
with the baton and caught him
in the mouth on the way down.

38:34.921 --> 38:37.097
That's very impressive.

38:37.140 --> 38:39.186
But you're on restricted duty.

38:39.229 --> 38:42.276
You're not supposed to be
on the street making collars.

38:42.320 --> 38:44.713
What are you gonna do,
toss me off the job?

38:46.759 --> 38:49.501
I'm not looking for pity.

38:49.544 --> 38:52.852
Or a handout of a desk job.

38:55.898 --> 38:58.466
I don't want to stay
where I'm not wanted.

39:00.207 --> 39:02.949
I'm not gonna
sue the department.

39:07.954 --> 39:10.435
So it's all or nothing.

39:12.698 --> 39:15.483
I've got applications
out to New Haven,

39:15.527 --> 39:17.877
Newark and the Philly PDs.

39:20.009 --> 39:21.446
If you could reach out...

39:21.489 --> 39:23.056
Reach out how?

39:23.099 --> 39:25.145
[chuckles] Like,
"I got this great detective,

39:25.188 --> 39:27.800
but I can't use her
'cause she's in a wheelchair"?

39:32.718 --> 39:34.241
[sighs]

39:34.284 --> 39:37.505
