For free.

39:41.640 --> 39:43.642
I know that.

39:44.643 --> 39:47.254
What if you had to have
a third detective with you

39:47.297 --> 39:48.821
when you were in the field?

39:50.388 --> 39:52.346
I could live with that.

39:52.390 --> 39:54.696
