your safety

39:54.740 --> 39:57.786
and that of your fellow officers
at all times?

39:57.830 --> 40:00.398
I know what I can
and can't do out there.

40:01.616 --> 40:06.142
What if you had to make
weekly reports to me

40:06.186 --> 40:08.406
about your progress?

40:16.283 --> 40:18.459
[sighs]

40:18.503 --> 40:20.069
You'll be the first.

40:20.113 --> 40:23.203
Make it work
so others can follow.

